<p><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: rgb(0, 176, 240); font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px; widows: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">台湾总统府开放时间</span></strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px; widows: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></p>
